{
  "video_id": "mgcjr1yz7ow",
  "title": "The surprising ingredient that makes businesses work better | Marco Alver√†",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13870.0,
      "end_time": 16506.0,
      "text": "For me, it was not being invited to a friend&#39;s wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17184.0,
      "end_time": 19334.0,
      "text": "At first, I didn&#39;t really mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19358.0,
      "end_time": 22200.0,
      "text": "I thought he was having a small reception."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22440.0,
      "end_time": 25497.0,
      "text": "But then I kept meeting people who were going to the same wedding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25521.0,
      "end_time": 27965.0,
      "text": "and they weren&#39;t as close to the groom as I was ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29192.0,
      "end_time": 30679.0,
      "text": "and I felt left out."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30703.0,
      "end_time": 31989.0,
      "text": "That really sucked."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32119.999999999996,
      "end_time": 33552.0,
      "text": "It felt really unfair."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34813.0,
      "end_time": 39312.0,
      "text": "For my daughters, Lipsi and Greta, it was last week."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40124.0,
      "end_time": 42702.0,
      "text": "They were taking turns massaging their mom&#39;s back"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42726.0,
      "end_time": 44814.0,
      "text": "with a toy for back rubs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44838.0,
      "end_time": 48130.0,
      "text": "and then one of the girls felt that the other girl had a longer go."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48604.0,
      "end_time": 50411.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when I walk into the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50435.0,
      "end_time": 53685.0,
      "text": "to find Greta in a rage, shouting, \"That&#39;s not fair!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53709.0,
      "end_time": 55674.0,
      "text": "and Lipsi in tears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55698.0,
      "end_time": 57656.0,
      "text": "and my wife holding a stopwatch"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57680.0,
      "end_time": 62158.0,
      "text": "to make sure that each girl had precisely one minute on the toy."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63963.0,
      "end_time": 68740.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re anything like me or my girls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68764.0,
      "end_time": 71470.0,
      "text": "the last thing that upset you"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71495.0,
      "end_time": 73764.0,
      "text": "probably also had to do with unfairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74756.0,
      "end_time": 78288.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because unfairness triggers us so strongly"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78312.0,
      "end_time": 79820.0,
      "text": "that we can&#39;t think straight."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80446.0,
      "end_time": 82469.0,
      "text": "We become afraid and suspicious."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83826.0,
      "end_time": 85937.0,
      "text": "Our unfairness antennae stick up."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87533.0,
      "end_time": 89438.0,
      "text": "We feel pain, and we walk away."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90479.0,
      "end_time": 94289.0,
      "text": "Unfairness is one of the defining issues of our society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94314.0,
      "end_time": 97449.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s one of the root causes of polarization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97474.0,
      "end_time": 99137.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s bad news for business."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100477.0,
      "end_time": 104589.0,
      "text": "At work, unfairness makes people defensive and disengaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105419.0,
      "end_time": 112380.0,
      "text": "A study shows that 70 percent of workers in the US are disengaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 112404.0,
      "end_time": 114150.0,
      "text": "and this is costing the companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114400.0,
      "end_time": 118552.0,
      "text": "550 billion dollars a year every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118576.0,
      "end_time": 122916.0,
      "text": "This is, like, half the total spent on education in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 123476.0,
      "end_time": 126410.0,
      "text": "This is the size of the GDP of a country like Austria."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 128255.0,
      "end_time": 131582.0,
      "text": "So removing unfairness and promoting fairness"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131606.0,
      "end_time": 132811.0,
      "text": "should be our priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 133969.0,
      "end_time": 135741.0,
      "text": "But what does it mean in practice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135765.0,
      "end_time": 138715.0,
      "text": "Is it about more rules? Is it about systems?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138740.0,
      "end_time": 140496.0,
      "text": "Is it about equality?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140520.0,
      "end_time": 144932.0,
      "text": "Well, partly, but fairness is more interesting than rules and equality."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 145471.0,
      "end_time": 147677.0,
      "text": "Fairness works in surprising ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 148669.0,
      "end_time": 153757.0,
      "text": "15 years ago, I left a US investment bank"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 153781.0,
      "end_time": 158678.0,
      "text": "to join a large Italian state-owned oil company."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158702.0,
      "end_time": 159954.0,
      "text": "It was a different world."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 160487.0,
      "end_time": 162835.0,
      "text": "I thought the key to getting the best performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 162859.0,
      "end_time": 164757.0,
      "text": "was a risk-reward system"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164781.0,
      "end_time": 168964.0,
      "text": "where you could give the high performers bonuses and promotions"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168988.0,
      "end_time": 171591.0,
      "text": "and give the underperformers something to worry about."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172435.0,
      "end_time": 176442.0,
      "text": "But in this company, we had fixed salaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 176466.0,
      "end_time": 177656.0,
      "text": "and lifelong jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 178903.0,
      "end_time": 180382.0,
      "text": "Careers were set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 180406.0,
      "end_time": 182840.0,
      "text": "so my toolkit wasn&#39;t very effective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182864.0,
      "end_time": 184116.0,
      "text": "and I was frustrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 184867.0,
      "end_time": 190580.0,
      "text": "But then I saw that this company was producing some pockets of excellence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 190820.0,
      "end_time": 192201.0,
      "text": "areas in which they beat the competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192225.0,
      "end_time": 194646.0,
      "text": "in very tough, competitive sectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 194670.0,
      "end_time": 196384.0,
      "text": "This was true in trading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196408.0,
      "end_time": 198527.0,
      "text": "in project management --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198551.0,
      "end_time": 200399.0,
      "text": "it was very true in exploration."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200926.0,
      "end_time": 204195.0,
      "text": "Our exploration team was finding more oil and gas"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204219.0,
      "end_time": 206970.0,
      "text": "than any other company in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206878.0,
      "end_time": 208280.0,
      "text": "It was a phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208649.0,
      "end_time": 211537.0,
      "text": "Everyone was trying to figure out how this was possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211561.0,
      "end_time": 213778.0,
      "text": "I thought it was luck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213802.0,
      "end_time": 217650.0,
      "text": "but after each new discovery, that became less and less likely."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 218215.0,
      "end_time": 221500.0,
      "text": "So did we have a special tool? No."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 222635.0,
      "end_time": 225721.0,
      "text": "Did we have a killer application that no one else had? No."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 226844.0,
      "end_time": 230950.0,
      "text": "Was it one genius who was finding oil for the whole team?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 230119.0,
      "end_time": 232547.0,
      "text": "No, we hadn&#39;t hired a senior guy in years."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234680.0,
      "end_time": 236658.0,
      "text": "So what was our secret sauce?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 237723.0,
      "end_time": 239845.0,
      "text": "I started looking at them really carefully."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 239869.0,
      "end_time": 241256.0,
      "text": "I looked at my friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 241280.0,
      "end_time": 243686.0,
      "text": "who drilled seven dry wells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243710.0,
      "end_time": 246495.0,
      "text": "writing off more than a billion dollars for the company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246519.0,
      "end_time": 248200.0,
      "text": "and found oil on the eighth."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248865.0,
      "end_time": 250190.0,
      "text": "I was nervous for him ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 252491.0,
      "end_time": 254470.0,
      "text": "but he was so relaxed."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 254611.0,
      "end_time": 256890.0,
      "text": "I mean, these guys knew what they were doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257410.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260338.00000000003,
      "text": "And then it hit me: it was about fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 261502.0,
      "end_time": 263217.0,
      "text": "These guys were working in a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263241.0,
      "end_time": 266360.0,
      "text": "where they didn&#39;t need to worry about short-term results."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 266539.0,
      "end_time": 271630.0,
      "text": "They weren&#39;t going to be penalized for bad luck or for an honest mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 271770.0,
      "end_time": 274762.0,
      "text": "They knew they were valued for what they were trying to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 274786.0,
      "end_time": 276320.0,
      "text": "not the outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 276560.0,
      "end_time": 279560.0,
      "text": "They were valued as human beings. They were part of a community."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 279800.0,
      "end_time": 281691.0,
      "text": "Whatever happened, the company would stand by them."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 281715.0,
      "end_time": 284688.0,
      "text": "And for me, this is the definition of fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 284712.0,
      "end_time": 288513.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s when you can lower those unfairness antennae, put them at rest."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 288537.0,
      "end_time": 289967.0,
      "text": "Then great things follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290376.0,
      "end_time": 294970.0,
      "text": "These guys could be true to their purpose, which was finding oil and gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294645.0,
      "end_time": 298248.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t have to worry about company politics or greed or fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 299814.0,
      "end_time": 302339.0,
      "text": "They could be good risk-takers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 302363.0,
      "end_time": 304862.0,
      "text": "because they weren&#39;t too defensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 304886.0,
      "end_time": 307592.0,
      "text": "and they weren&#39;t gambling to take huge rewards."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308583.0,
      "end_time": 311590.0,
      "text": "And they were excellent team workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311528.0,
      "end_time": 313149.0,
      "text": "They could trust their colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313173.0,
      "end_time": 315313.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t need to look behind their backs."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 316293.0,
      "end_time": 318627.0,
      "text": "And they were basically having fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 318651.0,
      "end_time": 320452.0,
      "text": "They were having so much fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320476.0,
      "end_time": 322660.0,
      "text": "one guy even confessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322684.0,
      "end_time": 326340.0,
      "text": "that he was having more fun at the company Christmas dinner"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 326580.0,
      "end_time": 327866.0,
      "text": "than at his own Christmas dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327890.0,
      "end_time": 330111.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 330135.0,
      "end_time": 335216.0,
      "text": "But these guys, essentially, were working in a fair system"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 335240.0,
      "end_time": 337802.0,
      "text": "where they could do what they felt was right"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 337826.0,
      "end_time": 340636.0,
      "text": "instead of what&#39;s selfish, what&#39;s quick, what&#39;s convenient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 340660.0,
      "end_time": 343537.0,
      "text": "and to be able to do what we feel is right"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 343561.0,
      "end_time": 347457.0,
      "text": "is a key ingredient for fairness, but it is also a great motivator."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 349187.0,
      "end_time": 352840.0,
      "text": "And it wasn&#39;t just explorers who were doing the right thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352639.0,
      "end_time": 358723.0,
      "text": "There was an HR director who proposed that I hire someone internally"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 358747.0,
      "end_time": 360661.0,
      "text": "and give him a managerial job."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 360685.0,
      "end_time": 363502.0,
      "text": "This guy was very good, but he didn&#39;t finish high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 363526.0,
      "end_time": 365780.0,
      "text": "so formally, he had no qualifications."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 366390.0,
      "end_time": 369724.0,
      "text": "But he was so good, it made sense, and so we gave him the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 370451.0,
      "end_time": 375325.0,
      "text": "Or the other guy, who asked me for a budget to build a cheese factory"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 375349.0,
      "end_time": 378931.0,
      "text": "next to our plant in Ecuador, in the village."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 378955.0,
      "end_time": 381813.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t make any sense: no one ever built a cheese factory."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 381837.0,
      "end_time": 385399.0,
      "text": "But this is what the village wanted, because the milk they had would spoil"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 385423.0,
      "end_time": 388180.0,
      "text": "before they could sell it, so that&#39;s what they needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 388420.0,
      "end_time": 389645.0,
      "text": "And so we built it."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 389670.0,
      "end_time": 391654.0,
      "text": "So in these examples and many others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 391678.0,
      "end_time": 394654.0,
      "text": "I learned that to be fair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 394678.0,
      "end_time": 398259.0,
      "text": "my colleagues and I, we needed to take a risk and stick our head out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 398283.0,
      "end_time": 400162.0,
      "text": "but in a fair system, you can do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 400186.0,
      "end_time": 401397.0,
      "text": "You can dare to be fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 402309.0,
      "end_time": 406951.0,
      "text": "So I realized that these guys and other colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 406975.0,
      "end_time": 411872.0,
      "text": "were achieving great results, doing great things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 411896.0,
      "end_time": 413856.0,
      "text": "in a way that no bonus could buy."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 414716.0,
      "end_time": 415955.0,
      "text": "So I was fascinated."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 415979.0,
      "end_time": 418169.0,
      "text": "I wanted to learn how this thing really worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 418194.0,
      "end_time": 421791.0,
      "text": "and I wanted to learn it also for myself, to become a better leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 421815.0,
      "end_time": 424644.0,
      "text": "So I started talking to colleagues, to coaches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424668.0,
      "end_time": 427170.0,
      "text": "to headhunters and neuroscientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 427194.0,
      "end_time": 428786.0,
      "text": "and what I discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 428810.0,
      "end_time": 431936.0,
      "text": "is that what these guys were up to and the way they worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 431960.0,
      "end_time": 434681.0,
      "text": "is really supported by recent brain science."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 435263.0,
      "end_time": 438628.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve also discovered that this can work at all levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 438652.0,
      "end_time": 439882.0,
      "text": "in any type of company."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 439906.0,
      "end_time": 443310.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t need the fixed salaries or the stable careers."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 444254.0,
      "end_time": 447803.0,
      "text": "This is because science shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447827.0,
      "end_time": 451794.0,
      "text": "that humans have an innate sense of fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 453390.0,
      "end_time": 455841.0,
      "text": "We know what is right and what is wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 455865.0,
      "end_time": 457793.0,
      "text": "before we can talk or think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 459900.0,
      "end_time": 461468.0,
      "text": "My favorite experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 461492.0,
      "end_time": 464221.0,
      "text": "has six-month old babies"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 464245.0,
      "end_time": 468540.0,
      "text": "watching a ball trying to struggle up a hill."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 468943.0,
      "end_time": 472969.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s a helpful, friendly square that pushes the ball up the hill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 472994.0,
      "end_time": 476239.0,
      "text": "and then a mean triangle pushes the ball back down."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 477420.0,
      "end_time": 479424.0,
      "text": "After watching this several times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 479448.0,
      "end_time": 481518.0,
      "text": "they ask the babies to pick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 481542.0,
      "end_time": 482883.0,
      "text": "to choose what to play with."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 482908.0,
      "end_time": 486201.0,
      "text": "They can pick a ball, a square or a triangle."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 487265.0,
      "end_time": 489455.0,
      "text": "They never pick up the triangle."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 489480.0,
      "end_time": 491344.0,
      "text": "All the babies want to be the square."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 493590.0,
      "end_time": 495662.0,
      "text": "And science also shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 495686.0,
      "end_time": 498448.0,
      "text": "that when we see or perceive fairness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 498472.0,
      "end_time": 502164.0,
      "text": "our brain releases a substance that gives us pleasure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 502189.0,
      "end_time": 503339.0,
      "text": "proper joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 504225.0,
      "end_time": 507177.0,
      "text": "But when we perceive unfairness, we feel pain ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 508601.0,
      "end_time": 509805.0,
      "text": "even greater pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 509829.0,
      "end_time": 512446.0,
      "text": "than the same type of pain as if I really hurt myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513275.0,
      "end_time": 517410.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because unfairness triggers the primitive, reptile part of our brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 517433.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520915.99999999994,
      "text": "the part that deals with threats and survival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 520941.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524449.0,
      "text": "and when unfairness triggers a threat, that&#39;s all we can think about."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 524473.0,
      "end_time": 527497.0,
      "text": "Motivation, creativity, teamwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 527521.0,
      "end_time": 529440.0,
      "text": "they all go way back."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 530119.0,
      "end_time": 532302.0,
      "text": "And it makes sense that we&#39;re wired this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 532326.0,
      "end_time": 533841.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re social animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 535000.0,
      "end_time": 537484.0,
      "text": "We need to be part of a community to survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 538134.0,
      "end_time": 540222.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re born so helpless"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 540246.0,
      "end_time": 543452.0,
      "text": "that someone needs to look after us until we&#39;re maybe 10 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 543476.0,
      "end_time": 545722.0,
      "text": "so our brain evolves towards food."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 545746.0,
      "end_time": 547635.0,
      "text": "We need to be in that community."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 547659.0,
      "end_time": 550236.0,
      "text": "So whether I like it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 553130.0,
      "text": "not being invited to the friend&#39;s wedding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 553154.0,
      "end_time": 556147.0,
      "text": "my lizard brain is generating the same response"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 556171.0,
      "end_time": 559190.0,
      "text": "as if I&#39;m about to be pushed out from my community."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 560763.0,
      "end_time": 565650.0,
      "text": "So science explains quite nicely why fairness is good"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 565890.0,
      "end_time": 567462.0,
      "text": "and why unfairness makes us really defensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 567486.0,
      "end_time": 571100.0,
      "text": "but science also shows that in a fair environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 571250.0,
      "end_time": 574100.0,
      "text": "not only do we all want to be the square,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 574124.0,
      "end_time": 576209.0,
      "text": "but we tend to be the square,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 576233.0,
      "end_time": 579733.0,
      "text": "and this allows other people to be fair in turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 579758.0,
      "end_time": 582264.0,
      "text": "This creates a beautiful fairness circle."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 583934.0,
      "end_time": 585616.0,
      "text": "But while we start off fair ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 586934.0,
      "end_time": 591997.0,
      "text": "one drop of unfairness contaminates the whole pool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 592210.0,
      "end_time": 595140.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately, there&#39;s plenty of drops in that pool."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 596606.0,
      "end_time": 600567.0,
      "text": "So our effort should be to filter out"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 600591.0,
      "end_time": 602687.0,
      "text": "as much unfairness as we can from everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 602711.0,
      "end_time": 605473.0,
      "text": "starting from our communities, starting from our companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 606687.0,
      "end_time": 612235.0,
      "text": "I worry about this a lot because I lead a team of 3,000 excellent people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 612259.0,
      "end_time": 616529.0,
      "text": "and the difference between 3,000 happy, motivated team workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 616553.0,
      "end_time": 619536.0,
      "text": "and 3,000 clock-watchers is everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 621154.0,
      "end_time": 626507.0,
      "text": "So the first thing I try to do in my fairness crusade"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 626531.0,
      "end_time": 629877.0,
      "text": "is to try to take myself out of the equation."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 629901.0,
      "end_time": 631997.0,
      "text": "That means being aware of my own biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 632210.0,
      "end_time": 634670.0,
      "text": "For example, I really like people who say yes"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 634695.0,
      "end_time": 635933.0,
      "text": "to whatever I suggest."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 635957.0,
      "end_time": 637302.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 637326.0,
      "end_time": 639354.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not very good for the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 639378.0,
      "end_time": 641856.0,
      "text": "and not very good for anyone who has different ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 641880.0,
      "end_time": 646120.0,
      "text": "So we try to actively promote a culture of diversity of opinions"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 646144.0,
      "end_time": 647829.0,
      "text": "and diversity of character."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 647853.0,
      "end_time": 650234.0,
      "text": "The second thing we do is a little more procedural."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 650259.0,
      "end_time": 653963.0,
      "text": "We look at all the rules, the processes, the systems in the company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 653987.0,
      "end_time": 657583.0,
      "text": "the ones we use to take decisions and allocate resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 657607.0,
      "end_time": 660970.0,
      "text": "and we try to get rid of anything that&#39;s not very clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 660994.0,
      "end_time": 662844.0,
      "text": "not very rational, doesn&#39;t make sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 662868.0,
      "end_time": 665179.0,
      "text": "and we also try to fix anything that&#39;s limiting"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 665203.0,
      "end_time": 667866.0,
      "text": "the transfer of information within the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 667890.0,
      "end_time": 671178.0,
      "text": "We then look at the culture and the motivation for the same reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 671202.0,
      "end_time": 673917.0,
      "text": "But my point is that however hard you look at the rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 673941.0,
      "end_time": 676564.0,
      "text": "the processes, the systems -- and we have to do that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 676588.0,
      "end_time": 678257.0,
      "text": "but however hard we look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 678282.0,
      "end_time": 681742.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re never going to do enough to get to the real essence of fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 681766.0,
      "end_time": 685924.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because the last mile of fairness requires something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 687330.0,
      "end_time": 689600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about what people&#39;s emotions are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 689624.0,
      "end_time": 691187.0,
      "text": "what their needs are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 691211.0,
      "end_time": 693830.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s going on in their private lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 693854.0,
      "end_time": 695289.0,
      "text": "what society needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 696994.0,
      "end_time": 699757.0,
      "text": "These are all questions and elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 699781.0,
      "end_time": 703631.0,
      "text": "that are very hard to put into a spreadsheet, into an algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 703655.0,
      "end_time": 706877.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very hard to make them part of our rational decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 706902.0,
      "end_time": 710538.0,
      "text": "But if we miss these, we&#39;re missing key important points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 710562.0,
      "end_time": 712861.0,
      "text": "and the outcome is likely to feel unfair."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 714180.0,
      "end_time": 718347.0,
      "text": "So we should cross-check our decisions with our fairness center switched on."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 719502.0,
      "end_time": 722858.0,
      "text": "Is it right that this guy should get the job he&#39;s really hoping to get?"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 723414.0,
      "end_time": 725716.0,
      "text": "Is it right that this guy should be fired?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 727273.0,
      "end_time": 730471.0,
      "text": "Is it right that we should be charging so much for this product?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 732129.0,
      "end_time": 733629.0,
      "text": "These are tough questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 735241.0,
      "end_time": 739122.0,
      "text": "But if we take the time to ask ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 739146.0,
      "end_time": 743247.0,
      "text": "whether the rational answer is the right one ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 744529.0,
      "end_time": 747386.0,
      "text": "we all know deep inside what the answer is."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 747410.0,
      "end_time": 749210.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve known since we were babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 750975.0,
      "end_time": 753315.0,
      "text": "And to know what the right answer is"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 753339.0,
      "end_time": 755227.0,
      "text": "is pretty cool for decision-making."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 757130.0,
      "end_time": 759847.0,
      "text": "And if we turn on our hearts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 759871.0,
      "end_time": 762514.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the key to getting the real best out of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 762538.0,
      "end_time": 765181.0,
      "text": "because they can smell it if you care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 765205.0,
      "end_time": 768302.0,
      "text": "and only when you really care will they leave their fears behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 768326.0,
      "end_time": 770133.0,
      "text": "and bring their true selves to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 771731.0,
      "end_time": 774340.0,
      "text": "So if fairness is a keystone of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 774364.0,
      "end_time": 777291.0,
      "text": "why isn&#39;t every leader making it their priority?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 778190.0,
      "end_time": 780947.0,
      "text": "Wouldn&#39;t it be cool to work in a company that was more fair?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 782492.0,
      "end_time": 785670.0,
      "text": "Wouldn&#39;t it be great to have colleagues and bosses"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 785910.0,
      "end_time": 789183.0,
      "text": "that were selected and trained for fairness and for character"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 789207.0,
      "end_time": 791439.0,
      "text": "and not based on 60-year-old GMATs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 793225.0,
      "end_time": 795630.0,
      "text": "Wouldn&#39;t it be nice to be able to knock on the door"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 795654.0,
      "end_time": 797375.0,
      "text": "of a Chief Fairness Officer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 798172.0,
      "end_time": 800899.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll get there, but why is it not happening now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 801502.0,
      "end_time": 803837.0,
      "text": "Well, partly, it&#39;s because of inertia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 803861.0,
      "end_time": 807180.0,
      "text": "partly, it&#39;s because fairness isn&#39;t always easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 807420.0,
      "end_time": 808843.0,
      "text": "It requires judgment and risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 809741.0,
      "end_time": 812241.0,
      "text": "Drilling that eighth well was a risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 813336.0,
      "end_time": 816415.0,
      "text": "Promoting the guy who didn&#39;t finish high school was a risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 817164.0,
      "end_time": 819997.0,
      "text": "Building a cheese factory in Ecuador was a risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 821354.0,
      "end_time": 825173.0,
      "text": "But fairness is a risk worth taking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 825197.0,
      "end_time": 827753.0,
      "text": "so we should be asking ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 827777.0,
      "end_time": 830930.0,
      "text": "where can we take this risk?"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 831310.0,
      "end_time": 835277.0,
      "text": "Where can we push ourselves a little bit further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 835302.0,
      "end_time": 838261.0,
      "text": "to go beyond what&#39;s rational and do what&#39;s right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 839865.0,
      "end_time": 841160.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 841400.0,
      "end_time": 846658.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}